snippet.title: Eat Mostly Fats
snippet.description:
THANK YOU SO MUCH FOR WATCHING AND SUPPORTING US! 
Dr Nadir Ali is now offering Online Consultations 
Email us for more info and to schedule a session at contact@eatmostlyfat.com 
Website: www.eatmostlyfat.com 
Facebook group: http://bit.ly/eatmostlyfatsfb\
Thank you!
EMF Team


**All videos on this channel are edited and uploaded by Melissa that works with Dr Nadir Ali, since he is busy with his cardiology practice, rounding at the hospital, and doing research for future videos and talks this channel is managed by her.**
